2006-03-15  Viktor Mihajlovski  <mihajlov@dyn-9-152-143-45.boeblingen.de.ibm.com>

	* repos.c: 
	Bug 1450216: Fall back to bubblesort if quicksort recursion level gets
	to high. Fixed value comparison for floats.

2006-03-14  Viktor Mihajlovski  <mihajlov@dyn-9-152-143-45.boeblingen.de.ibm.com>

	* plugin/metricXen.c: 
	Bug 1449628: Fixed segfault on System z (and probably POWER).

	* mrepos.h, mreposl.c, repos.c, mreposp.c: 
	Bug 1449436: Changed repository metric retrieval interface to internally
	process the resource information. This allows to retrieve the metric values
	for a set of resources in one call to the repository.
	Use binary search in resource localization and insertion code ,
	which enhances the effort from O(n**2) to O(n*log n) for metric insertions.
	Changed local repository data structures for faster access by maintaining
	per-resource value lists. This costs 4% more memory but changes the
	effort from O(n**2) to O(log n) for current metric data retrievals.

	* reposd.c, rreg.c, rrepos.c, comms/rcserv_ip.c:
	Bug 1449436: Optimized various string and memory operations with respect
	to path lengths.

